25/08/2008
TIRANA, Albania -- The ruling Democratic Party (DP) will hold elections within its organisation starting next month, deputy leader Astrit Patozi announced on Sunday (August 24th). Speaking at a press conference, Patozi said the internal elections are aimed at preparing for general parliamentary elections next summer. (Koha Jone, Shqip - 25/08/08; Top Channel, Klan - 24/08/08)
